title: Cisco Meraki: Device Status
agents: cisco_meraki
catalog: os/services
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check plugin monitors the device status.

 It is OK, if the status is {online}, it is CRIT if the status is {altering}
 and it is WARN if the status is {offline} or {dormant}.

 In order to make this check plugin work you have to configure the ruleset for
 the special agent {{Cisco Meraki}}.

 The check plugin can be configured via the corresponding WATO rule
 {{Cisco Meraki Organisation Device Status}}.

discovery:
 One service per organisation ID is created.
